Package game.mc

Class MCAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.mc.MCAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Action, java.io.Serializable
    public final class MCAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Action
    Specifies the type of the action for the Matrian Chess game. That is a pair of positions. The first is the position of a figure on the table, the second is a position where to move it.
